  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effect of heart rate on cardiac index in patients
      with or without left ventricular hypertrophy. The study will be conducted in postoperative
      heart surgery patients with a pacemaker.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
